      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>a. I, Athanasios, who
performed every civic duty in this, my own country, and lived abroad
for many years, and visited many peoples, and sailed every sea as far
as Ocean, and saw every race of men, and was kept safe, I prayed to
God to reach my country and to be buried by the traces of the holy
<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">martyrs</supplied>, <seg cert="low">so that</seg> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">I should have an advocate in</supplied> the day of
judgement <gap reason="lost"/> Jesus Christ, Father, <gap reason="lost"/> <supplied reason="lost">receive my</supplied>
soul <gap reason="lost"/></ab>
        <ab>b. Here I lie, Athanasios,
who lived abroad for many years, and visited many peoples. and sailed
every sea as far as Ocean, and saw every race of men, and was kept
safe, I prayed to God to <supplied cert="low" reason="lost">reach my country</supplied> and <supplied cert="low" reason="lost">to be buried by the
traces</supplied> of the holy <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">martyrs</supplied> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">so that I should have an advocate in</supplied>
the day of judgement <gap reason="lost"/>.</ab>
      </div>

